null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014640, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah! This is verily a place wherein one who misses Your mercy must never expect to find it elsewhere. None can be more miserable that one who visits this place, bearing hope, but leaves it with disappointment. O Allah! I do seek Your protection against evil return, hopeless retirement, and hard interrogation when I am called to account.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Be-shak yeh woh baargah hai keh jo yahan Teri rehmat haasil na kar saka, woh kahi haasil na kar paayega aur us se bada bad-bakht koi nahi jo yahan ummeed le kar aaya to na-kaam palat gaya. Ay Ma’bood! Yaqeenan mai Teri panah leta hu buri tarah palatne na-ummeed ke saath laut kar jaane se aur hisaab mein sakhti se.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! بے شک یہ وہ بارگاہ ہے کہ جو یہاں تیری رحمت حاصل نہ کر سکا کہیں حاصل نہ کر پائے گا اور اس سے بڑا بد بخت کوئی نہیں جو یہاں امید لے کر آیا تو ناکام پلٹ گیا اے معبود! یقینًا میں تیری پناہ حاصل کرتا ہوں بری طرح پلٹنے نا امیدی کے ساتھ لوٹ کر جانے سے اور حساب میں سختی سے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA INNA HAAZAA MASHHA-DOON LAA YARJOO MAN FAA-TATHO FEEHE RAHMATO-KA AN YANAALA-HAA FEE GHAIRE-HI WA LAA AHA-DOON ASHQAA MENIM-RE-IN QASADA-HU MO-A’MMELAN FA-AABA A’NHO KHAA-E-BAN. ALLAAHUMMA INNEE A-OO’ZO-BEKA MIN SHARRIL EYAA-BE WA KHAI-BATIL MUNQALA-BE WAL MONAAQA-SHA-TE I’NDAL HESAABE.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنَّ هٰذَا مَشْهَدٌ لَا يَرْجُوْ مَنْ فَاتَتْهُ فِيْهِ رَحْمَتُكَ اَنْ يَنَالَهَا فِيْ غَيْرِهٖ وَلَا اَحَدٌ اَشْقٰى مِنِ امْرِئٍ قَصَدَهٗ مُؤَمِّلًا فَاٰبَ عَنْهُ خَآئِبًا۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّيْ اَعُوْذُ بِكَ مِنْ شَرِّ الْاِيَابِ وَخَيْبَةِ الْمُنْقَلَبِ وَالْمُنَاقَشَةِ عِنْدَ الْحِسَابِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014641, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "It is too far from You, O my Lord! That after You matched the obedience to Your (visited) representative to the obedience to You, the loyalty to him to the loyalty to You, and the disobedience to him to the disobedience to You, You may then shock with despair one who has visited him and who has undergone remoteness from homeland to come to his grave! By Your Honor, O my Lord! I swear; my conscience can never even think of so, because all hearts always have excellent ideas about You.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Aur ay Parwardigaar aisa na ho keh Tu apne wali ki ita’at apni ita’at ke saath, unki dosti apni dosti ke saath aur unki na-farmaani apni na-farmaani ke saath laazim kar de, phir unke zaaer aur dur ke shehro’n se ba-mushkil unki qabr par aane waale ko maayoos kare. Ay Parwardigaar Teri izzat ki qasam keh mera dil us baat par yaqeen nahi rakhta kyu’n keh dil to Teri maher-baani aur achchhaayi ki taraf ishaara karta hai.", "Urdu": "اور اے پروردگار! ایسا نہ ہو کہ تو اپنے ولی کی اطاعت اپنی اطاعت کے ساتھ ان کی دوستی اپنی دوستی کے ساتھ اور ان کی نا فرمانی اپنی نا فرمانی کے ساتھ لازم کر دے پھر ان کے زائر اور دور کے شہروں سے بہ مشکل ان کی قبر پر آنے والے کو مایوس کرے اے پروردگار! تیری عزّت کی قسم کہ میرا دل اس بات پر یقین نہیں رکھتاکیوں کہ دل تو تیری مہربانی اور اچھائی کی طرف اشارہ کرتے ہیں۔", "RArabic": "WA HAA-SHAKA YAA RABBE AN TUQRE-NA TAA-A’TA WALIYYE-KA BE-TA-A’TEKA WA MAWAA-LAATE-HI BE-MOWAA-LAATEKA WA MA’SEYATE-HI BE-MA’SEYATE-KA SUMMA TO-YESA ZAA-E-RAHU WAL MO-HAMMELA MIM BO’DIL BALAA-DE ILAA QABRE-HI WA I’ZZATE-KA YAA RABBE LAA YAN-A’QEDO A’LAA ZAALE-KA ZAMEE-REE IZ-KAANA-TIL QOLOO-BO ILAIKA BIL JAMEELE TO-SHEE-RO.", "ArabicText1": "وَحَاشَاكَ يَا رَبِّ اَنْ تُقْرِنَ طَاعَةَ وَلِيِّكَ بِطَاعَتِكَ وَمُوَالَاتِهٖ بِـمُوَالَاتِكَ وَمَعْصِيَتِهٖ بِمَعْصِيَتِكَ ثُمَّ تُؤْيِسَ زَآئِرَهٗ وَالْمُتَحَمِّلَ مِنْۢ بُعْدِ الْبِلَادِ اِلٰى قَبْرِهٖ وَعِزَّتِكَ يَا رَبِّ لَا يَنْعَقِدُ عَلٰى ذٰلِكَ ضَمِيْرِيْ اِذْ كَانَتِ الْقُلُوْبُ اِلَيْكَ بِالْجَمِيْلِ تُشِيْرُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": n